# --- Real Casper testnet (visible on https://testnet.cspr.live) ---

# 1. cd ../../casper-contracts && cargo odra build

#    (needs nightly Rust + wasm32 target; wasm copied to wasm/settlement_registry.wasm)

# 2. cd ../backend/relay && npm run generate:casper-key

# 3. Fund public key at https://testnet.cspr.live/tools/faucet

# 4. npm run deploy:casper

# 5. Restart relay — deploy script sets CASPER_DRY_RUN=false automatically

#

# CASPER_DRY_RUN=false

# CSPR_NODE_URL=https://node.testnet.casper.network/rpc

# CSPR_CHAIN_NAME=casper-test

# CASPER_CONTRACT_PACKAGE_HASH=hash-...

# CSPR_SECRET_KEY_PATH=./keys/relay_secret_key.pem

# CASPER_EXPLORER_BASE_URL=https://testnet.cspr.live

# CASPER_PAYMENT_MOTES=2500000000

